{"tid":2326071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白登：我是所有美國人的總統","createTime":"2020-12-15T04:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T02:07:56.000Z","uid":184679,"like":17,"dislike":230,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"1b08fc12a1920c4373c7f9973c5a2a8d72104772","tid":2326071,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:59:55.000Z","msg":"美國選舉人團選出拜登為下任美國總統，拜登發表全國電視演說時說，現在是翻開新的一頁，是團結一致和癒合的時候。 <br />\n<br />\n拜登：「我將會是所有美國人的總統，不管有沒有投票給我，我都會努力工作。我們眼前有很多緊急的工作，包括控制新冠病毒疫情，為全國民眾接種疫苗，我們要提供經濟援助給最有需要的民眾。」<br />\n<br />\n拜登在演說中提到，特朗普陣營提出多項訴訟挑戰選舉結果，但沒有一項訴訟有足夠的證據支持，有幾個州雖然重新點票，但結果最後亦得到認證。<br />\n<br />\n拜登表示，自己贏得的選舉人票，跟特朗普在四年前大選時的得票相同，當時特朗普自稱取得壓倒性勝利，拜登期望特朗普也能承認今次的選舉結果。<br />\n<br />\n美國國會將會在下月6日完成點算和公布選舉人票結果，之後拜登會在20日就職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416651&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416651%26refer%3DShare&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGOoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=5e11262e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416651%26refer%3DShare&h=11e4c75a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416651&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"fd52ffed0cd653bed2563950d7ac747b8ff2729b","tid":2326071,"uid":70487,"like":49,"dislike":2,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T05:01:08.000Z","msg":"賀錦鯉 &gt; 拜燈"},{"pid":"587dd1e20c9e0e92fdaa619cc2f1621febf68806","tid":2326071,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T05:01:33.000Z","msg":"已贏"},{"pid":"b4e3030af7f2c1250739db0efec7ee95138fc0ef","tid":2326071,"uid":14918,"like":29,"dislike":4,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T05:03:08.000Z","msg":"用詞咁專政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2859413384338903662d35ab523b547cdfb6083","tid":2326071,"uid":37596,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":